{"tid":2260380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【12港人】元朗區議員促公開定翼機航行紀錄 民政專員拉隊離場兼熄咪","createTime":"2020-10-27T13:49:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T17:03:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1348a1ba218b370ee97c024b78e0a2bad202eb5f","tid":2260380,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:49:50.000Z","msg":"（獨媒報導）元朗區議會今日召開會議，有民主派區議員提出兩項動議，分別要求港府為被內地扣押的12港人提供一切人道需要，以及公開希臘貨船Angelic Glory與飛行服務隊定翼機的航行及雷達紀錄。元朗民政事務專員袁嘉諾和其他部門官員隨即離場，拒絕參與討論。直至討論「建議由區議會撥款成立元朗區議會網上直播頻道」議程時，民政事務專員及官員才返回會議室。<br />\n<br />\n民政熄咪 民主派自備擴音機續開會<br />\n<br />\n民政專員離場同時熄咪，區議會主席黃偉賢問「係咪有小露寶（無線便攜式流動擴音機）呀？」，民主派區議員遂以擴音機繼續會議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078445&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=f7c94c6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078445&h=843373a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078445</a>"},{"pid":"c217fc5724685b5ca7cd1ac2fdbb1e89217905dd","tid":2260380,"uid":280525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3992cf800a4eb1274a03beaa24fb225fbe7470","tid":2260380,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c217fc5724685b5ca7cd1ac2fdbb1e89217905dd","tid":2260380,"uid":280525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T13:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji